                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/9910" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">STR-2490</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">719 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">“数智安防运维平台”助力企业数智化转型与核心竞争力提升</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">&quot;The Digital and Intelligent Security Operation Platform&quot; Helps Enterprises Achieve Digital and Intelligent Transformation and Enhance Core Competitiveness</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">邓万里，王保生，乔鹏亮，单丽薇，李宗洪，洪婉雯，李璐颖</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">广州工商学院vip</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">广州市百用软件科技有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">其他</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中小型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规划计划部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">11 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">决策型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">数智安防；运维平台；数智化转型；核心竞争力</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Digital and intelligent security; Operation and maintenance platform; Digital and intelligent transformation; Core competence</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">在2025年的BIM技术国际交流会上，A公司陈总汇报了实施“数智安防运维平台”的原因和经验。安防维保业务是A公司主营业务，但传统模式已经难以适应市场发展需求，出现一系列的问题。数字技术可以提高安防运维的专业化水平，提升企业的核心竞争力，适应目标市场的未来发展需求。为此，公司逐步推进安防维保业务的数智化转型。2023年，“数智安防运维平台”项目正式立项，平台将安防维保管理平台与物联网、托管运营结合，打破传统点对点服务模式的局限，提升资源整合和集约化运营程度，并拓展服务项目，从而满足客户多样化需求。平台运行成效显著：与2023年相比较，2024年公司销售业绩同比增长21.5%，运营成本下降6.7%，区域市场覆盖扩大14.8%；不但赢得用户好评，提升了企业核心竞争力，还为行业和企业发展提供了可以模仿和复制的经验范例。本案例适用于《战略管理》课程中关于企业的数字化转型、企业战略转型等章节或模块的教学，适用于管理相关专业的研究生和MBA、EMBA学生，也可用于企业管理人员与数字化和战略转型相关的培训课程。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">At the BIM Technology International Exchange Conference in 2025, Mr. Chen from company A presented the reasons and experiences for implementing the &quot;Digital and Intelligent Security Maintenance Platform&quot;. Security maintenance is the primary business of company A, but the traditional model has been unable to meet the market&#39;s development needs, resulting in a series of problems. Digital technology can enhance the professional level of security maintenance, improve the core competitiveness of the enterprise, and adapt to the future development needs of the target market. Therefore, the company gradually promoted the digital transformation of the security maintenance business. In 2023, the &quot;Digital and Intelligent Security Maintenance Platform&quot; project was officially approved. The platform combines security maintenance management with the Internet of Things and managed operations, breaking the limitations of the traditional point-to-point service model. It improves the degree of resource integration and centralized operation, expanding service projects to meet the diversified needs of customers. The platform has achieved remarkable results: Compared to 2023, the company&#39;s sales performance in 2024 increased by 21.5% year-over-year, operating costs decreased by 6.7%, and regional market coverage expanded by 14.8%. Not only did it win user praise and enhance the core competitiveness of the enterprise, but it also provided an exemplary model that can be imitated and replicated for the development of the industry and enterprises. This case is applicable for teaching the chapters or modules related to enterprise digital transformation and enterprise strategic transformation in the &quot;Strategic Management&quot; course. It is suitable for postgraduate students and MBA/EMBA students majoring in management, and can also be used in training courses for enterprise managers on digital transformation.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2023</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《战略管理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">数智化转型的驱动因素和路径、企业核心竞争力构建、转型成效理论、战略启示理论</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2025-09</td>
